    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Hanzo holds an elevated sightline to threaten one-shot picks with Storm Arrow bursts or a fully-drawn shot, using Lunge to reposition between angles.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>His arrows have significant travel time and drop, so fast-moving flankers and hitscan heroes at close range consistently beat him in a straight fight.</p>"
